---
layout: layouts/base.njk
bodyClass: home-alt
---
<section class="home-banner" aria-labelledby="home-title">
  <div class="container home-banner-inner">
    <div class="home-banner-copy">
      <p class="home-eyebrow">快连官方 · 快连下载</p>
      <h1 id="home-title">全平台客户端一站获取</h1>
      <p class="home-banner-lead">{{ heroLead or site.description }}</p>
      <div class="home-banner-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-cta-main" href="/download.html">进入下载中心</a>
        <a class="btn btn-cta-ghost" href="/blog/">查看全部教程</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <figure class="home-banner-figure">
      <img src="{{ '快连官方 客户端' | bingImg }}" alt="快连官方客户端界面预览" width="520" height="320" loading="eager">
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-platforms" id="section-download" aria-label="各平台下载">
  <div class="container">
    <ul class="platform-strip">
      <li>
        <a href="/download.html#windows">
          <span class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">Win</span>
          <span class="platform-label">Windows</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/download.html#macos">
          <span class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">Mac</span>
          <span class="platform-label">macOS</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/download.html#android">
          <span class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">And</span>
          <span class="platform-label">Android</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/download.html#ios">
          <span class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">iOS</span>
          <span class="platform-label">iPhone / iPad</span>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-main" id="section-updates">
  <div class="container home-main-grid">
    <div class="home-updates">
      <header class="home-updates-head">
        <h2>最新文章更新</h2>
        <a class="home-more-link" href="/blog/">更多教程 →</a>
      </header>
      <ol class="update-list">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
        {% if loop.index <= 12 %}
        <li class="update-item">
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateZh }}">{{ post.date | dateZh }}</time>
          <div class="update-body">
            <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            {% if post.data.category %}
            <span class="update-cat">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </li>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    </div>

    <aside class="home-aside" aria-label="快捷入口">
      <div class="aside-card aside-download">
        <h2>快连官方下载</h2>
        <p>四端安装包与版本说明集中在下载中心。</p>
        <a class="btn btn-cta-main btn-block" href="/download.html">打开下载中心</a>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card" id="section-version">
        <h2>版本与兼容</h2>
        <p>Windows 需 64 位；macOS 区分 arm64 / x64；移动端建议预留 200MB 空间。</p>
        <a href="#section-verify">安装包核对说明</a>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card" id="section-verify">
        <h2>获取建议</h2>
        <p>请通过本站下载中心获取客户端，核对文件大小与版本后再安装。</p>
        <a href="/blog/#cat-faq">常见问题</a>
      </div>
      <nav class="aside-tags" aria-label="热门标签">
        <h2>热门标签</h2>
        <div class="tag-cloud">
          {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
          {% if loop.index <= 6 %}
          <a href="/tags/{{ tag | slug }}/">{{ tag }}</a>
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </nav>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-bottom-strip">
  <div class="container home-bottom-inner">
    <div id="section-compat">
      <strong>系统兼容</strong>
      <p>建议将系统更新至官方支持的稳定版后再安装快连官方客户端。</p>
    </div>
    <div id="section-scenarios">
      <strong>使用场景</strong>
      <p>办公、家庭多设备与移动端出行，可按<a href="/blog/">教程</a>完成配置。</p>
    </div>
    <div id="section-faq">
      <strong>问题排查</strong>
      <p>连接异常与报错说明见<a href="/blog/#cat-faq">常见问题</a>栏目。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
